        <updateDate>2007-12-15T15:56:41Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) exclude participations and residuals from the dollar limitation on the taxpayer election to expense qualified film and television production costs; (2) allow amortization of costs ineligible for expensing; and (3) make such expensing election permanent.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
